{"image_id": "SYK_2016_page_11", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "STRYKER CORPORATION                                                                                                                          2016 Form 10-K", "bbox": [75.0, 22.3, 1196.0, 45.6]}, {"text": "Dollar amounts in millions except per share amounts or as otherwise specified.", "bbox": [79.2, 1557.6, 628.7, 1573.9]}, {"text": "9", "bbox": [1183.5, 1557.6, 1191.7, 1573.9]}, {"text": "ITEM 7.", "bbox": [81.2, 112.4, 146.9, 133.3]}, {"text": "MANAGEMENT’S DISCUSSION AND ANALYSIS OF FINANCIAL CONDITION AND RESULTS OF OPERATIONS.", "bbox": [208.3, 112.4, 1182.3, 133.3]}, {"text": "ABOUT STRYKER", "bbox": [75.0, 150.4, 235.8, 171.4]}, {"text": "Stryker Corporation is a global leader in medical technology and", "bbox": [75.0, 179.2, 623.9, 200.1]}, {"text": "offers a diverse array of innovative medical technologies including", "bbox": [75.0, 201.7, 623.9, 222.6]}, {"text": "orthopaedic, medical and surgical, and neurotechnology and spine", "bbox": [75.0, 224.2, 624.0, 245.1]}, {"text": "products to help people lead more active and satisfying lives.", "bbox": [75.0, 246.7, 585.7, 267.6]}, {"text": "Our goal is to achieve sales growth at the high-end of the medical", "bbox": [75.0, 275.4, 624.0, 296.4]}, {"text": "technology (MedTech) industry and maintain our capital allocation", "bbox": [75.0, 297.9, 623.9, 318.9]}, {"text": "strategy that prioritizes: (1) Acquisitions, (2) Dividends and (3)", "bbox": [75.0, 320.4, 624.0, 341.4]}, {"text": "Share repurchases.", "bbox": [75.0, 342.9, 238.6, 363.9]}, {"text": "Overview of 2016", "bbox": [75.0, 371.7, 228.2, 392.6]}, {"text": "In 2016 we achieved reported sales growth of 13.9%. Excluding the", "bbox": [75.0, 400.4, 624.0, 421.4]}, {"text": "impact of acquisitions, sales grew 6.4% in constant currency, in line", "bbox": [75.0, 422.9, 623.9, 443.9]}, {"text": "with our ongoing goal to grow organic sales at the high-end of", "bbox": [75.0, 445.4, 624.0, 466.4]}, {"text": "MedTech. We reported net earnings of $1,647 in 2016 and achieved", "bbox": [75.0, 467.9, 624.0, 488.9]}, {"text": "15.1% growth in net earnings per diluted share(1). Excluding the", "bbox": [75.0, 487.4, 624.0, 511.4]}, {"text": "impact of certain items, we achieved adjusted net earnings of", "bbox": [75.0, 512.9, 624.0, 533.9]}, {"text": "$2,194 and growth of 13.3% in adjusted net earnings per diluted", "bbox": [75.0, 535.4, 624.0, 556.4]}, {"text": "share(1).", "bbox": [75.0, 554.9, 147.2, 578.9]}, {"text": "We continued our capital allocation strategy by investing $4,332 in", "bbox": [75.0, 586.7, 624.0, 607.6]}, {"text": "acquisitions, paying $568 in dividends to our shareholders and", "bbox": [75.0, 609.2, 623.9, 630.1]}, {"text": "using $13 for share repurchases.", "bbox": [75.0, 631.7, 349.1, 652.6]}, {"text": "In 2016 we completed the acquisitions of Sage Products, LLC", "bbox": [656.2, 156.7, 1205.2, 177.6]}, {"text": "(Sage) for total consideration of approximately $2,875, Physio-", "bbox": [656.2, 179.2, 1200.0, 200.1]}, {"text": "Control International, Inc. (Physio) for total net consideration of", "bbox": [656.2, 201.7, 1205.2, 222.6]}, {"text": "approximately $1,299 and the Synergetics neuro portfolio", "bbox": [656.2, 224.2, 1205.2, 245.1]}, {"text": "(Synergetics). Sage develops, manufactures and distributes", "bbox": [656.2, 246.7, 1205.2, 267.6]}, {"text": "intensive care disposable products. Physio develops, manufactures", "bbox": [656.2, 269.2, 1205.2, 290.1]}, {"text": "and markets monitors/defibrillators, AEDs and CPR-assist devices", "bbox": [656.2, 291.7, 1205.2, 312.6]}, {"text": "along with data management and support services. The acquired", "bbox": [656.2, 314.2, 1205.2, 335.1]}, {"text": "Synergetics products include the Malis generator, Spetzler Malis", "bbox": [656.2, 336.7, 1205.2, 357.6]}, {"text": "disposable forceps and our existing Sonopet tips and RF generator.", "bbox": [656.2, 359.2, 1205.2, 380.1]}, {"text": "Refer to Note 5 to our Consolidated Financial Statements for further", "bbox": [656.2, 381.7, 1205.2, 402.6]}, {"text": "information.", "bbox": [656.2, 404.2, 759.4, 425.1]}, {"text": "In January 2017 we sold $500 of senior unsecured notes, and in", "bbox": [656.2, 432.9, 1205.2, 453.9]}, {"text": "2016 we sold $3,500 of senior unsecured notes and repaid all $750", "bbox": [656.2, 455.4, 1200.0, 476.4]}, {"text": "of our senior unsecured notes that were due in September 2016.", "bbox": [656.2, 477.9, 1205.2, 498.9]}, {"text": "Refer to Note 9 to our Consolidated Financial Statements for further", "bbox": [656.2, 500.4, 1205.2, 521.4]}, {"text": "information.", "bbox": [656.2, 522.9, 759.4, 543.9]}, {"text": "RESULTS OF OPERATIONS", "bbox": [75.0, 712.1, 320.2, 733.0]}, {"text": "Percent Net Sales", "bbox": [813.3, 753.6, 936.5, 769.9]}, {"text": "Percentage Change", "bbox": [1036.0, 753.6, 1172.2, 769.9]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [506.7, 774.4, 539.1, 790.7]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [594.2, 774.4, 626.6, 790.7]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [681.7, 774.4, 714.1, 790.7]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [777.5, 774.4, 809.9, 790.7]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [865.0, 774.4, 897.4, 790.7]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [946.3, 774.4, 978.7, 790.7]}, {"text": "2016/2015", "bbox": [1021.8, 774.4, 1090.7, 790.7]}, {"text": "2015/2014", "bbox": [1117.6, 774.4, 1186.5, 790.7]}, {"text": "Net sales", "bbox": [81.2, 795.2, 145.3, 811.5]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [485.4, 795.2, 493.5, 811.5]}, {"text": "11,325 $", "bbox": [517.1, 795.2, 581.0, 811.5]}, {"text": "9,946 $", "bbox": [612.7, 795.1, 668.5, 811.5]}, {"text": "9,675", "bbox": [700.1, 795.2, 736.6, 811.5]}, {"text": "100.0%", "bbox": [787.9, 795.2, 837.4, 811.5]}, {"text": "100.0%", "bbox": [875.4, 795.2, 924.9, 811.5]}, {"text": "100.0%", "bbox": [950.4, 795.2, 999.9, 811.5]}, {"text": "13.9%", "bbox": [1062.7, 795.2, 1104.1, 811.5]}, {"text": "2.8%", "bbox": [1166.7, 795.2, 1199.9, 811.5]}, {"text": "Gross profit", "